name: TracingOptions

properties.name: parent
properties.description: The object's container.

properties.name: typename
properties.description: The class name of the object.

properties.name: preset
properties.description: The name of the preset in use. Read-only.

properties.name: viewMode
properties.description: The visualization mode.

properties.name: tracingMode
properties.description: The tracing mode: color, gray, black and white.

properties.name: tracingColorTypeValue
properties.description: Color Type used for tracing, TracingLimitedColor or TracingFullColor .

properties.name: palette
properties.description: The color palette (Library) name used for tracing. Use 'Document Library' or any other imported library name.

properties.name: colorGroup
properties.description: The color group name used for tracing. Use 'All' or any color group name available in color Palette (library).

properties.name: tracingColors
properties.description: Maximum number of colors allowed for tracing when TracingColorTypeValue is TracingLimitedColor.

properties.name: colorFidelity
properties.description: ColorFidelity when TracingColorTypeValue is TracingFullColor.

properties.name: threshold
properties.description: The threshold value for a black and white mode tracing.

properties.name: grayLevels
properties.description: The gray levels for a grayscale mode tracing..

properties.name: pathFidelity
properties.description: Path fidelity for tracing.

properties.name: cornerFidelity
properties.description: Corner fidelity for tracing.

properties.name: noiseFidelity
properties.description: Specifies minimum area of pixels to be vectorized.

properties.name: tracingMethod
properties.description: Method for tracing, either abutting or adjoining paths.

properties.name: fills
properties.description: Tracing with fills. Fills, Strokes or both must be on.

properties.name: strokes
properties.description: Tracing with strokes. Fills, Strokes or both must be on.

properties.name: maxStrokeWeight
properties.description: Maximum stroke weight (stroke only).

properties.name: snapCurveToLines
properties.description: Controls whether to snap curve to lines.

properties.name: ignoreWhite
properties.description: Controls whether to ignore white fill color. Works only if TracingMethod is TracingMethodAbutting and mode is Black and white.

methods.name: storeToPreset
methods.description: Store options to a preset kAiVectorizeSuite. Will overwrite an existing (unlocked) preset if names match.

description: Tracing options that guide the tracing process.
